show.description: Contract lover banne wali Raha, aur uska ruthless hero Rudra, is intense romance thriller mein dono ki kahani hai. Betrayal, passion, aur ek aisa rishta jo pyaar aur saza ke beech jhoolta hai. Dekhiye “Soft Cruelty” , jahan har lamha hai dangerously romantic.
